안녕하세요 친구들~~~!

저는 쯔위 사랑!

I just have SOOO much Korean vocabulary to build and learn!

I love Tzuyu!
Of course I love all the girls of Twice! 🫰🏻

I really like how they made the title "aboutTZU"  like "aboutYOU" sounding like "aboutChew"! 👍🏻
So many people have had difficulty with how to pronounce her name. It sounds like Chewy! Very easy!
Since saying "about you" quickly can sound like "about chew" the title "aboutTZU" fits very well!
Very creative! 👍🏻😁

author: @PoussinNoNeko
text:
PAIRING LIST:
Run Away: americano
= iced or warm, where you can feel the delicate emotions of when love first blossoms

Heartbreak In Heaven: lemonade
= sweet and sour, joy and pain

Lazy Baby: cherry coke
= free-spirited atmosphere and addictive melody, on a day where you don't wanna do anything

Losing Sleep: chamomile tea
= because you become sleepless longing for someone, it's a contrasting taste

One Love: peach-ade (like lemonade I guess)
= because peach blossoms mean "I'm yours", a song referring to Twice and Once's love

Fly: melon soda
= picked by Chae for the fairytale-like lyrics
